WEBVTT

00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:30.216
And so I did further research
to find out more

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:33.176
about the beneficial uses of this weed.

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:36.616
Out of the several,
one struck me the most.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:39.736
It was the use of the plant
for handicrafts.

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:42.096
And I thought, "What a great idea."

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:44.496
Personally, I love handicrafts,

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:49.176
especially handicrafts
that are woven around a story.

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:53.816
And so I thought, "This could be
easily deployed within the communities

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:57.376
without the requirement
of technical skills."

00:03:57.400 --> 00:04:02.040
And I thought to myself,
"Three simple steps to a mega solution."